OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1780319467
OL,3,CGirl, 13, dies after going into River
OL,4,CWharfe
OL,6,FA 13-year-old girl has died after
OL,7,Fbeing pulled from a North Yorkshire
OL,8,Friver.
OL,10,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,11,FRiver Wharfe near Burnsall in the
OL,12,FSkipton area after a teenage girl was
OL,13,Freported missing at around 6.30pm on
OL,14,FSunday 31 May.
OL,16,FNorth Yorkshire police say she was
OL,17,Fpulled from the water and taken to
OL,18,Fhospital by air ambulance.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/3
