OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1780319467
OL,3,CGirl, 13, dies after going into River
OL,4,CWharfe
OL,6,FA spokesperson for the force said:
OL,7,F"Despite the efforts of members of the
OL,8,Fpublic and medical staff at the scene
OL,9,Fand in hospital, she sadly died.
OL,11,F"At this stage we are not in a
OL,12,Fposition to release her identity.
OL,14,F"Our thoughts remain with her family
OL,15,Fat this very distressing time and we
OL,16,Fask members of the public and the
OL,17,Fmedia to respect the family's privacy
OL,18,Fand allow them to grieve in peace.
OL,20,F"Our thanks go to the members of the
OL,21,Fpublic who helped."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/3
